  <brief_title>Foot/Ankle at 7T MRI</brief_title>
  <official_title>High-Resolution MR Imaging (7 Tesla) Findings of the Plantar Plate Compared With Current Clinical Standard Sequences (1.5 or 3 Tesla) and Surgical Reference Standard</official_title>
  <sponsors>
