  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      -  To evaluate standard clinical sequences for 7 Tesla MRI of the foot and/or ankle to
           improve detailed depiction of the complex anatomy of this region.

        -  To evaluate various pathologies of the foot and/or ankle (plantar plate tears, Morton
           neuroma, tendon tears, ligament tears etc.).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
